This paper deals with computer vision algorithms for object pose estimation, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of reinforcement learning to optimize the pose estimation system suggests that it could also be categorized under robotics (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of a CNN, which is a common tool in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the focus on resource allocation and efficiency suggests that it could also be categorized under systems and control (cs.SY).
